description.en: BIDZ Coin has a unique approach to the online commerce and real-world applications. You can use your BIDZ Coin to buy real products or services throughout our ecosystem. Upon launch of BIDZ Coin, the team plans to build a bridge between crypto, commerce, and real world applications.
